name: Subtle Spirits Full Circle (feat. Gianluca Franzese)

metadata.name: Full Circle (feat. Gianluca Franzese) #8 of 22
metadata.description:
Subtle Spirits' third NFT Whiskey release Full Circle features the artwork of Gianluca Franzese. This NFT is limited to 22 Collector Editions. Each will include unlockable content containing instructions to redeem an archival print and a bottle featuring the artwork. Each bottle is wax dipped and hand decorated with 23k gold lustered lines. Both the print and bottle are numbered and signed by the artist. 

You must be 21+ to receive the bottle. Bottles ship from the United States. Because of the laws and logistics around shipping spirits, we are unable to ship to some countries. You are responsible for knowing the shipping laws and rules for your country of origin.
